snippet.title: VIDeo PHOBIA - Trailer for Demo. (Official Video).
snippet.description:
The Game on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3344030/

VIDeoPHOBIAYou are in a room without windows or doors. The TV dimly illuminates the room. What is this, a box? How to open it? 

After solving the riddle, you find the TV remote control. Click... a door appeared. 

You step into the darkness and hear laughter... turn around and find out what's behind the screen.
